               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; a few lines on the incipit page, alternating with black lines; two initial lines of each subsection of the text; elements of punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals; some words like kǝfl (e.g., fols. 9ra, 13rb, 24ra), fǝkkare (e.g., fols. 121rb, 121va, 122ra), rabǝʿ (e.g., fols.122vc, 124rb, 126va), yǝbe (e.g., fols. 130ra, 130va), tǝʿǝzaz (e.g., fols. 132vc, 133ra).</rubric>
